nl.bioinf.diseasefinderSpring.bodyfeatures

Enum BodyFeature

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<BodyFeature>
      • nl.bioinf.diseasefinderSpring.bodyfeatures.BodyFeature
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BodyFeature>

    public enum BodyFeature
extends java.lang.Enum<BodyFeature>
    BodyFeature is the enum which specifies all the main features of a disease.
